title: Understanding Cube Functions
text: Cube functions are used in data analysis, especially when dealing with multidimensional data. They help in performing complex calculations and data retrieval from data cubes.

hintAnswer: a set of advanced analytic functions that you can use with multidimensional data, also called data cubes
